// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2597913344" "Colonel Duray"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3664920972" "Colonel Virgil Duray has had a long time to culture his hatred for the heroes he holds responsible for the Rikti War. In combat with heroes, he won't give an inch."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1178625081" "I know you're here, assassin.  You might as well show your face."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3308031867" "You're not getting away this time, {HeroName}.  Not on my watch, at least!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P1085644015" "I have to say, I wasn't expecting you to be the one."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P4048694312" "You're going to have to try harder than that."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P824597341" "I eat punks like you for breakfast, kid."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3990079198" "I've gotta give it my all.  For their memory."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P2329560035" "Nooooooooo!"
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P1127119350" "Let's see how you like being a forgotten casualty."
// Script Variable Greeting :
"P2729859857" "Well, well, {HeroName}."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1171662970" "Before you take me in, talk to me at least."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1803031166" "Wolf Spider Infiltrator"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2162279758" "You may be smart, Duray, but not smart enough to keep your mouth shut."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3100920666" "So now it's time for you and your friends to meet those veterans you care so much about."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P3604716471" "You never should have stuck your nose where it belongs."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2439538195" "I'll take you down as easily as I did those vets."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P221649184" "Don't think you can stop me."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P2985995389" "Mission accomplished!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P986391717" "<em grief>HAHAHA!  You think you've beaten me?<br><br>Go ahead, hero.  Take me in.<br><br>I'll be out the next day.  AGAIN!<br><br>You'll never stop us because you don't have the steel to do what needs to be done."

